# StatusCard Design System

The StatusCard is a premium glassmorphic component designed for the bottom-right corner of the application.

## Colors

### Light Mode
| Element | Property | Value | Tailwind Class |
|---------|----------|-------|----------------|
| Background | Glass | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)` | `bg-white/40` |
| Border | Stroke | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)` | `border-white/50` |
| Label | Text | `#3B82F6` (Blue 500) | `text-blue-500` |
| Title | Text | `#1E293B` (Slate 800) | `text-slate-800` |
| Subtext | Text | `#64748B` (Slate 500) | `text-slate-500` |
| Dot | Indicator | `#22C55E` (Green 500) | `bg-green-500` |

### Dark Mode
| Element | Property | Value | Tailwind Class |
|---------|----------|-------|----------------|
| Background | Glass | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)` | `bg-black/40` |
| Border | Stroke | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)` | `border-white/10` |
| Label | Text | `#94A3B8` (Slate 400) | `text-slate-400` |
| Title | Text | `#F8FAFC` (Slate 50) | `text-slate-50` |
| Subtext | Text | `#94A3B8` (Slate 400) | `text-slate-400` |
| Dot | Indicator | `#22C55E` (Green 500) | `bg-green-500` |

## Components
- **Icon Container**: Circular container with subtle inner shadow.
- **Glass Effect**: Backdrop filter with blur and transparency.
- **Typography**: Inter (System Default).
